{"word":"παραρρέω","slug":"παραρρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραρρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ρεύσομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-ερρύην</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>-ερρύηκα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to flow beside</i> or <i>past</i>, <el>τόπον</el> or <el>παρὰ τόπον</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <i>to drift away</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to slip out</i> or <i>off</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to slip in unawares</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}